<BaseLayout title="Terms — RETARDMAX" description="Terms for using the RETARDMAX board, groups, and paid credits."><section class="space-y-6"><h1 class="font-display text-6xl">TERMS.</h1><p class="text-white/50">Effective July 18, 2026.</p><div class="card space-y-5 p-5 text-white/70"><h2 class="font-display text-3xl text-white">Use of the board</h2><p>You must be able to form a binding contract and are responsible for your account and posts. Do not use RETARDMAX for doxxing, harassment, threats, fraud, illegal activity, or content you do not have the right to share.</p><h2 class="font-display text-3xl text-white">Moderation and visibility</h2><p>Public posts, votes, and groups may be visible to other users. We may remove content, restrict accounts, or suspend access when needed to protect people and the service.</p><h2 class="font-display text-3xl text-white">Credits and availability</h2><p>Paid credits and subscriptions are shown at checkout and processed by Stripe. The service is provided as available and may change. Questions: <a class="text-flame" href="mailto:support@retardmax.app">support@retardmax.app</a>.</p></div></section></BaseLayout>
